sketch.compiler.ast.core

Class Program

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FENode
      • sketch.compiler.ast.core.Program

  • public class Program
extends FENode
    An entire Sketch program. This includes all of the program's declared Packages and optionally some directives. It consequently has Lists of packages (as Package objects) and some compiler directives.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
